  "Face overrides shared by every Rosé Pine variant.
All entries reference palette role names (rose, gold, foam, pine,
iris, love, text, subtle, muted, base, surface, overlay,
highlight-low, highlight-med, highlight-high, and the doom-themes
spectrum bg/fg/base0..base8/grey/red/orange/green/yellow/blue/
dark-blue/magenta/violet/cyan/dark-cyan/teal).  Each theme file
binds those names to its variant-specific colors before passing
this list to `def-doom-theme'.")

(defmacro doom-rose-pine--def-theme (name docstring palette)
  "Define a Rosé Pine theme variant.
NAME is the theme symbol, DOCSTRING the description, PALETTE the
variable bindings (passed as `def-doom-theme's defs)."
  `(def-doom-theme ,name ,docstring
     ,palette
     ,doom-rose-pine--face-spec))

